# The /ask (Ask Me) page sends question notifications + confirmations by
# authenticating directly to Gmail's SMTP as 123kanishka@gmail.com (see
# OWNER_EMAIL in src/app/api/ask/route.ts) — no custom sending domain needed.
#
# To get an app password: enable 2-Step Verification on that Google account,
# then create an "App Password" at https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# (choose "Mail" as the app) and paste the 16-character value below.
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=
